locality: South Province, Chikwawa District. Lengwe National Park baobab woodland.
Selous Game Reserve, T6 Matambwe, riverine forest.
Dodoma -iringa road 25 miles from Dodoma central

4 km from Makiungu on rd to Misughaa, then 3.2 km along new rd to Mkunguakihendo. Top of escarpment, irregular SE-facing slopes. Thinned miombo dom. by Julbernardia globiflora mostly 4-5m high, & very thin canopy of Brachystegia microphylla at 15m.
Sadani Ward, Ihanzutwa Village, Ikelele Forest.

10½ km on rd from Misughaa to Kwa Mtoro. Broadly rolling hills, light brown ?silty sand. Somewhat thinned miombo woodland 15(-20)m dom. by Julbernardia globiflora with some Brachystegia spiciformis & in the undercanopy Strychnos & Combretum zeyheri.
MACHINGA Liwonde National Park. Elev. 480 m.
